# Installation of GHC 7.10.1

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution  
cd $HOME/Downloads  

wget https://www.haskell.org/ghc/dist/7.10.1/ghc-7.10.1-x86_64-unknown-linux-deb7.tar.bz2   
tar xvfj ghc-7.10.1-x86_64-unknown-linux-deb7.tar.bz2  

cd ghc-7.10.1  

# install to  
mkdir $HOME/GHC-compiler/bin/ghc-7.10.1  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/GHC-compiler/bin/ghc-7.10.1  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd $HOME/Downloads  
rm -rfv ghc-7.10.1*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
switchghc 7.10.1 
~~~